organization.description: CurleyGu00c7u00d6s House of Style, Inc. / Hope Relief Food Bank is a grass roots 501 (c) 3 non-profit organization established in August 2001. Our mission is to improve the quality of life for low-to-moderate income individuals and families, the elderly, the homebound , the abused, HIV/AIDS infected, youth, and youth-at-risk by providing bulk food product to these needy residents and serving as a neighborhood outreach ministry. Services approximately 1,000 clients weekly by providing them with bulk food products, nutritional flyers on diabetes, high blood pressure, job vacancies and sponsor financial education and literacy seminars.
organization.name: CURLEY'S HOUSE OF STYLE, INC.
